nodes.text: Erica Lindbeck (born May 29, 1992) is an American voice actress best known for being the official voice of the last generation of Barbie dolls. She has also done voice work for many animes and provided the voice of Black Cat in Insomniac Games' popular Spider-Man video game.
In 2019, Lindbeck had a voice role in the Star Wars video game Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order.
